# Step 1

1. In order to earn free bitcoin you need to install a bitcoin wallet. A bitcoin wallet is like a normal wallet that holds your bitcoins.
    You can install bitcoin wallets on different platforms; like on a phone or a computer.
  i. Mobile Wallets - I prefer these wallets but you can find more at wwww.bitcoin.org/en/choose-your-wallet.
    a. breadwallet - www.breadwallet.com
       breadwallet is free and the most secure bitcoin wallet on apple mobile devices. I personally have used it in the past. It is a very easy to use
       bitcoin wallet, you can send and recieve transactions with a couple of taps.
